  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Riot Ride is an <strong>arcade car-combat</strong> game with <strong>roguelike</strong> mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive a<strong> weaponized car</strong> through <strong>procedurally </strong>generated levels in a <strong>retro</strong>, <strong>Tron-like</strong> world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect <strong>blueprints </strong>and deliver them back safely while fending off a <strong>variety of hacked vehicles</strong> trying to end your run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.mp4?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless play styles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge <strong>weapons</strong> and buy <strong>passive items</strong> from the shop to survive. Use them to <strong>customize</strong> your car <strong>endlessly </strong>to further <strong>personalize your playstyle</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/a8b1bdfed7e07866b79429c096bd527d.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/a8b1bdfed7e07866b79429c096bd527d.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/a8b1bdfed7e07866b79429c096bd527d.mp4?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging bosses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face <strong>increasingly difficult bosses</strong>, each with <strong>unique attack patterns</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/cdcad9b6436f781bf5ad58a914486682.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/cdcad9b6436f781bf5ad58a914486682.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/cdcad9b6436f781bf5ad58a914486682.mp4?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perma death</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play, die, learn, and repeat</strong> until you confront the<strong> final villain</strong> in a brutal showdown to finally break free from the simulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/80de2a4b007b7b1534469e2ab8ef839f.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/80de2a4b007b7b1534469e2ab8ef839f.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/80de2a4b007b7b1534469e2ab8ef839f.mp4?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play up to 36 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use up to 17 unique weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight 8 unique enemy types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off 9 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you die, you lose all your progress</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Riot Ride is an <strong>arcade car-combat</strong> game with <strong>roguelike</strong> mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive a<strong> weaponized car</strong> through <strong>procedurally </strong>generated levels in a <strong>retro</strong>, <strong>Tron-like</strong> world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect <strong>blueprints </strong>and deliver them back safely while fending off a <strong>variety of hacked vehicles</strong> trying to end your run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.mp4?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless play styles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge <strong>weapons</strong> and buy <strong>passive items</strong> from the shop to survive. Use them to <strong>customize</strong> your car <strong>endlessly </strong>to further <strong>personalize your playstyle</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/a8b1bdfed7e07866b79429c096bd527d.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/a8b1bdfed7e07866b79429c096bd527d.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9