class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play up to 36 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use up to 17 unique weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight 8 unique enemy types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off 9 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you die, you lose all your progress</p></li></ul>",
